    "type": "npc",
    "sections": [
        {
            "name": "Description",
            "type": "section",
            "html": "Small, sly, and seemingly innocuous, evil halflings make perfect murderers."
        },
        {
            "name": "Lisanne Jelansil",
            "type": "section",
            "html": "At first, Lisanne saved her murderous attentions for those who slighted her in some small fashion. Now, she revels in death for death\u2019s sake rather than for vengeance only. Her reputation has grown with her crimes, and she increasingly plies her skills for pay as well as pleasure."
        }
    ],
